smartsheet               web. 全息片体；片体可以是参数化特征；张蓝纸
json pointer             json指针
result                   [n] 结果;成果;效果;成绩;产物;成效;收获;功;名堂;
-- separator between context and content. should be a single character string, like '-'. -- when separator is set, the context will only show up when there are at least 2 lines above cursorline.-- 上下文和内容之间的分隔符。应该是单个字符串，例如“-”。 -- 设置分隔符后，仅当光标线上方至少有 2 行时才会显示上下文。
-- separator between context and content. should be a single character string, like '-'. -- when separator is set, the context will only show up when there are at least 2 lines above cursorline.-- 上下文和内容之间的分隔符。应该是单个字符串，例如“-”。 -- 设置分隔符后，仅当光标线上方至少有 2 行时才会显示上下文。
enable = true, -- enable this plugin (can be enabled/disabled later via commands) multiwindow = false, -- enable multiwindow support. max lines = 0, -- how many lines the window should span. values <= 0 mean no limit. min window height = 0, -- minimum editor window height to enable context. values <= 0 mean no limit. line numbers = true, multiline threshold = 10, -- maximum number of lines to show for a single context trim scope = \"outer\", -- which context lines to discard if `max lines` is exceeded. choices: 'inner', 'outer' mode = \"cursor\", -- line used to calculate context. choices: 'cursor', 'topline' -- separator between context and content. should be a single character string, like '-'. -- when separator is set, the context will only show up when there are at least 2 lines above cursorline. separator = nil,enable = true, -- 启用此插件（可以稍后通过命令启用/禁用） multiwindow = false, -- 启用多窗口支持。 maxlines = 0, -- 窗口应跨越多少行。值 <= 0 表示没有限制。 min window height = 0, -- 启用上下文的最小编辑器窗口高度。值 <= 0 表示没有限制。行数= true，多行阈值= 10，--单个上下文显示的最大行数修剪范围=“外部”，--如果超过“最大行数”，则丢弃哪些上下文行。 options: 'inner', 'outer' mode = \"cursor\", -- 用于计算上下文的行。 options: 'cursor', 'topline' -- 上下文和内容之间的分隔符。应该是单个字符串，例如“-”。 -- 设置分隔符后，仅当光标线上方至少有 2 行时才会显示上下文。分隔符=零，
